thread.title: Sebastian James

author: Sebastian James
title: Sebastian James
text: Perception is reality and everything about Servcorp Chifley creates a very positive perception. From the opulence of the art deco inspired lobby to the spectacular views that greet you at the level 29 reception desk it really does leave a great first impression on colleagues and clients alike. All of this however would be redundant without the exceptional friendly yet highly professional services provided by the amazing girls that keep this place ticking. Great work Servcorp your miles ahead of your competition.
